\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
To, \u269\'0do si ale mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee potrebujeme e\u353\'61te dorie\u353\'61i\u357\'65 a \u269\'0do predkladan\u225\'e1 novela neobsahuje, by som zhrnula len v\~sum\u225\'e1ri, m\u225\'e1me prv\u233\'e9 \u269\'0d\u237\'edtanie, do jednotliv\u253\'fdch t\u233\'e9m a\~bodov. Predov\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdm naozaj vyrovna\u357\'65 platby \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu za poistencov \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu do rezervn\u233\'e9ho fondu, ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee v s\u250\'fa\u269\'0dasnosti neplat\u237\'ed 4,75 % ako v\u353\'61etci ostatn\u237\'ed poistenci, ale len 2 %, teda zabezpe\u269\'0di\u357\'65 vy\u353\'61\u353\'61\u237\'ed pr\u237\'edspevok \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu na d\u244\'f4chodky. Slovensko patr\u237\'ed medzi krajiny s najni\u382\'7e\u353\'61ou mierou prispievania \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu na d\u244\'f4chodky. Viac ako 80 % v\u253\'fddavkov hradia ob\u269\'0dania priamo z odvodov. Zv\u253\'fd\u353\'61en\u233\'e9 prispievanie napr\u237\'edklad z dan\u237\'ed zo spotreby by pritom zv\u253\'fd\u353\'61ilo solidaritu celkov\u233\'e9ho syst\u233\'e9mu. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Som presved\u269\'0den\u225\'e1, \u382\'7ee vstup do II. piliera pre mlad\u253\'fdch \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, pre bud\u250\'facu gener\u225\'e1ciu, ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee i samo ministerstvo vo svojich anal\u253\'fdzach potvrdilo, \u382\'7ee pre t\u250\'fato gener\u225\'e1ciu v princ\u237\'edpe z poh\u318\'3eadu dlhodob\u233\'e9ho mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9ho sporenia je II. pilier v\u253\'fdhodn\u253\'fd, urobi\u357\'65 vstup automaticky s mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65ou vyviazania sa v istej lehote z\~II. piliera. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Rovnako pova\u382\'7eujem za otvoren\u253\'fd probl\u233\'e9m postavenia invalidn\u253\'fdch d\u244\'f4chodcov. Z\u225\'e1kon nem\u225\'e1 v sebe obsiahnut\u233\'e9 rovnak\u233\'e9 podmienky  pre invalidn\u253\'fdch d\u244\'f4chodcov ako pre ostatn\u233\'e9 skupiny. Ak toti\u382\'7e pracuj\u250\'fa, platia poistn\u233\'e9 na invalidn\u233\'e9 poistenie, hoci z t\u253\'fdchto odvodov nikdy ni\u269\'0d ma\u357\'65 nebud\u250\'fa, ich odvody na starobn\u233\'e9 poistenie sa zhodnotia v bud\u250\'facom starobnom d\u244\'f4chodku len \u269\'0diasto\u269\'0dne alebo v\u244\'f4bec, z\u225\'e1rove\u328\'48 stratili n\u225\'e1rok na pr\u237\'edspevok \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu do II. piliera. Som presved\u269\'0den\u225\'e1, \u382\'7ee by sta\u269\'0dilo iba tro\u353\'61ku v\u244\'f4le a tieto ned\u244\'f4slednosti by sme mohli v z\u225\'e1kone odstr\u225\'e1ni\u357\'65. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Novela rie\u353\'61i aj probl\u233\'e9m v\u253\'fdpo\u269\'0dtu d\u244\'f4chodkov pre osoby, ktor\u233\'e9 poberaj\u250\'fa invalidn\u253\'fd d\u244\'f4chodok, \u269\'0di pred rokom 2004 mali roky, v ktor\u253\'fdch po cel\u253\'fd rok \u353\'61tudovali, boli na civilnej slu\u382\'7ebe alebo cel\u253\'fd rok mali takzvan\u233\'e9 n\u225\'e1hradn\u233\'e9 doby. Pravdou je, \u382\'7ee je to ist\u253\'fd pozit\u237\'edvny posun a rie\u353\'61enie ch\u253\'fdb z ostatnej novely, ale pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru iba \u269\'0diasto\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9. Novela rovnako men\u237\'ed podmienky pre priznanie invalidn\u253\'fdch d\u244\'f4chodkov. V priemere je to pozit\u237\'edvna zmena. Av\u353\'61ak pokia\u318\'3e m\u225\'e1me zmenu, ktor\u225\'e1 ist\u253\'fd \u269\'0das m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee prinies\u357\'65 zhor\u353\'61enie situ\u225\'e1cie a m\u225\'e1me mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 sa tomu vyhn\u250\'fa\u357\'65, potom by novela tak\u233\'e9to ustanovenie mohla obsahova\u357\'65. Ide toti\u382\'7e len o prechodn\u233\'e9 ustanovenie a pre t\u250\'fato \u269\'0das\u357\'65 invalidn\u253\'fdch  d\u244\'f4chodcov mohol plati\u357\'65 star\u253\'fd syst\u233\'e9m, pokia\u318\'3e je pre nich v\u253\'fdhodnej\u353\'61ie, ide o prechodn\u233\'e9 ustanovenie. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Novela \u271\'0falej neodstra\u328\'48uje diskrimin\u225\'e1ciu zamestnancov, ktor\u237\'ed popri pr\u225\'e1ci aj podnikaj\u250\'fa. Pokia\u318\'3e u\u382\'7e platia odvody zo zamestnania, maj\u250\'fa plati\u357\'65 aj minim\u225\'e1lne odvody z pr\u225\'e1ce popri zamestnan\u237\'ed, z\~podnikania. Toti\u382\'7e re\u382\'7eim, kedy im tak\u233\'e9to zdvojenie je odpusten\u233\'e9, sa vz\u357\'65ahuje len na ist\u233\'e9 vybran\u233\'e9 soci\u225\'e1lne skupiny, presne definovan\u233\'e9 profesie, vytv\u225\'e1ra to nerovnov\u225\'e1hu. V s\u250\'favislosti s pred\u314\'3a\u382\'7een\u237\'edm minim\u225\'e1lnej doby d\u244\'f4chodkov\u233\'e9ho poistenia, ktor\u233\'e9 je platn\u233\'e9 z 10 na 15 rokov, odpor\u250\'fa\u269\'0dam zv\u225\'e1\u382\'7ei\u357\'65 pred\u314\'3a\u382\'7ei\u357\'65 maxim\u225\'e1lnu dobu platenia poistn\u233\'e9ho \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tom za opatrovate\u318\'3eov a osobn\u253\'fdch asistentov a rodi\u269\'0dov z 12 tie\u382\'7e na 15 rokov, aby mali splnen\u253\'fd limit, ktor\u253\'fd je stanoven\u253\'fd v ostatnej novele z\u225\'e1kona o soci\u225\'e1lnom poisten\u237\'ed. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pani ministerka spom\u237\'ednala alebo sa vyjadrovala, \u382\'7ee zva\u382\'7euje v bud\u250\'facnosti oddeli\u357\'65 v\u253\'fd\u353\'61ku minim\u225\'e1lnych odvodov pre \u382\'7eivnostn\u237\'edkov od minim\u225\'e1lnej mzdy. Diskutovali sme o tom aj v soci\u225\'e1lnom v\u253\'fdbore. Prerok\u250\'favame z\u225\'e1kon o soci\u225\'e1lnom poisten\u237\'ed. Z \u250\'fast \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tneho tajomn\u237\'edka sme boli informovan\u237\'ed, \u382\'7ee sa pracovn\u225\'e1 skupina zaober\u225\'e1 touto t\u233\'e9mou a n\u225\'e1vrhom, \u269\'0d\u237\'edm by to mohlo by\u357\'65 nahraden\u233\'e9 a\~vymenen\u233\'e9. Mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee tak\u233\'e9to rie\u353\'61enie mohlo by\u357\'65 s\u250\'fa\u269\'0das\u357\'65ou tejto predkladanej novely o soci\u225\'e1lnom poisten\u237\'ed. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Preto si dovol\u237\'edme v druhom \u269\'0d\u237\'edtan\u237\'ed predlo\u382\'7ei\u357\'65 ist\u253\'fd rad pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'facich n\u225\'e1vrhov, vr\u225\'e1tane pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'faceho n\u225\'e1vrhu, o ktorom sa p\u244\'f4vodne hovorilo, \u382\'7ee bude novela prin\u225\'e1\u353\'61a\u357\'65 a\~obsahova\u357\'65, a to je ist\u253\'fd garantovan\u253\'fd minim\u225\'e1lny d\u244\'f4chodok, dovol\u237\'edm si v snemovni predstavi\u357\'65 ist\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1vrh tohto rie\u353\'61enia. }
